    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >决战苍穹2 是制作组和社区玩家向21年前所爱游戏的致敬之作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266430/extras/8feb790a098bf3a21d6a79b9b423ea5a.poster.avif?t=1728814720\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266430/extras/8feb790a098bf3a21d6a79b9b423ea5a.webm?t=1728814720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266430/extras/8feb790a098bf3a21d6a79b9b423ea5a.mp4?t=1728814720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这场星际角逐中，联盟和背叛并存，只有最敏锐的指挥官才能在太阳系的争夺战中脱颖而出。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入或创建军团，争取成为领袖，你的每个决定都会对紧张的政治和军事格局产生重大影响。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为军团长，你将拥有机会在派系内通过竞选，攀升至帝国的最高权力巅峰，成为帝国执政官。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >执政官可以指派各军团领袖担任要职，如情报大臣、外交大臣、防卫大臣和近卫御林长官等。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将体验最多每场50人的即时战略对抗，派系拥有实时动态领土，掌控情报和补给线至关重要。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据自己的技术路线和科技等级，自由改装和搭配超过2500种战斗配件以适应多变的前线战场。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collapsed Galaxy 1 源自十年前中文社区共创</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏离不开社区玩家们的贡献、支持与鼓励，欢迎访问官网查看这份珍贵名单。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266430/extras/45640274728a0e105535d8237fa21cfa.poster.avif?t=1728814720\" width=616 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266430/extras/45640274728a0e105535d8237fa21cfa.webm?t=1728814720\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266430/extras/45640274728a0e105535d8237fa21cfa.mp4?t=1728814720\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
